{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_08_03",
  "title": "井川葵 3話 いつか飛びたい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-aoi025.m4a",
      "text": "ステージに、光……\n……そうだ、光だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A stage… light…\n…That’s it‚ light!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.0619961422
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "楽曲とライティングを組み合わせるってことか？\nそれなら今までもやってきたと思うけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You mean combining the music with the lighting?\nBut we’ve done that before‚ haven’t we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7000009537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだけど、振り付けとライティングを\n完璧に合わせることまではやってなかっただろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ but we’ve never\nperfectly synchronized the choreography and lighting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6779558398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.9053297044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "例えば手を伸ばした方向にライトを走らせるとか\nバックに投影した映像がぶわっと広がるとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like having the lights follow our outstretched hands‚\nor having the projected images in the background expand dramatically.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7000009537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "タイミングがぴったり合えば\n凄くダイナミックな振り付けに見えそうじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If the timing is perfect‚\nit could look like incredibly dynamic choreography‚ don’t you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1000009537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.1456240655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……なるほど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.1456240655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "要は客席から大きく、軽やかに見えればいいんだから\n必ずしも僕達が限界まで動く必要はなかったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The point is to make it look big and dynamic from the audience’s perspective‚\nso we don’t necessarily have to push ourselves to the limit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.7000009537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.4406321924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "さて……やりたいことは決まったけど\nどうやって実現しようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now… I’ve decided on what I want to do‚\nbut how should we make it happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.0666650772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "あらかじめ僕達の手足にセンサーを付けておいて\nライトに追いかけてもらうのが一番楽なんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The easiest way would be to attach sensors to our limbs\nand have the lights follow us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.8333332698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.7822663387
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。ミクに会場中のライトを\nまとめて操作してもらうことって出来ないかなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s it. I wonder if we could have Miku\ncontrol all the lights in the venue.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7666666031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.7807472945
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、ミクなら『ネットワークに侵入！』とか\nSFみたいなことも簡単にやれそうじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know‚ with Miku‚ it feels like she could do sci-fi stuff\nlike that easily.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.5333332698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ミクはあくまでバーチャル・シンガーであって\n凄腕ハッカーとかそういうのじゃないからなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Miku is a virtual singer‚\nnot some kind of super hacker.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7333332698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、それもそうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ that’s true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0000009537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.661700058
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "葵が言うような、ステージの演者をトラッキングして\nライトや映像を投影する技術は、実際あるらしいけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard there’s actually technology that can track performers on stage\nand project lights and images based on their movements‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.4023888335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……今回のライブでは難しいだろうな\n特殊なカメラがいるはずだし、準備時間も足らない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but… it would be difficult to do it for this live show.\nWe’d need special cameras‚ and we don’t have enough time to prepare.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.9333332698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "ふむ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.6188203176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.0588274122
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "となると、ステージのバックの映像に\n僕達が完璧に合わせて踊るしかないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ we’ll just have to\ndance perfectly in sync with the images on the back screen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.8333403905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "ライトが追いついてこられないっていうなら\n僕達が合わせてあげないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If the lights can’t keep up‚\nwe’ll have to adjust to them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7031159084,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.8805053194
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "完璧に合わせるって……\nさらっと言ったけど、それだってかなり難しいだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Perfectly in sync…\nYou make it sound easy‚ but that would be extremely difficult.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.9333403905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "そうかなぁ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.5022965868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.3004139463
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "今度は無茶な動きにはしないし、本番までは数日あるし\nなんとかなるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not going to make them do any crazy movements this time‚ and we still have a few days until the actual performance‚\nso it’ll be fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.999701703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.326672383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（今、どこからともなく、こころの）\n（「葵さんの鬼！！」って声が聞こえた気がしたな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I think I just heard Kokoro’s voice from somewhere‚）\n（saying‚ “Aoi-san is a demon!”）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.4333398819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（……生きろ、こころ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Stay strong‚ Kokoro.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.712186388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.709479892
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "さて、それじゃホテルに戻ろうか\nライブ当日まで、やることが沢山出来たからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ let’s head back to the hotel.\nWe have a lot to do before the day of the live show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.6333358128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "……それに、僕もいい加減寒くなってきたよ\n指先もこんなに冷たくなっちゃってさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…And I’m getting cold.\nMy fingertips are so cold.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.966684405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.6765244362
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。君は温かそうだし、手を繋いでもいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Say‚ you look warm. Can I hold your hand?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.6765244362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
