      "text": "（北海道のファンの盛り上がりは、想像以上だな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The Hokkaido fans are even more enthusiastic than I imagined.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.1905028062,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7699.498147500009,
          "startTime": 176.8900009537
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（セトリも全部こなして、あとはアンコールだけ……）\n（……うわ。ミクを紹介した途端、凄い歓声だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（We’ve gotten through the entire setlist‚ and all that’s left is the encore…）\n（…Whoa. The cheers are incredible as soon as we introduce Miku.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.8333510716,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11599.983215400016,
          "startTime": 190.433334287
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_circularstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 183.4112286287
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "今日ここに来られたみんなは、ラッキーだったね\nアンコール一曲目は……新曲だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone who came here today is lucky.\nThe first song of the encore… is a new song!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.4000177383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi021.m4a",
      "text": "（ミクと僕達とで、みんなが楽しんでくれるようにって）\n（今日のために作った新曲……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Miku‚ us‚ so that everyone can enjoy it）\n（The new song we made for today…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.4666793187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi022.m4a",
      "text": "（……ああでも、一番楽しかったのは僕達かもね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Ah‚ but maybe we had the most fun.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.4333449681,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi023.m4a",
      "text": "（ずっとファンだったミクと、一緒に振り付けを考えて）\n（リハをこなすのは、最高に充実した時間だった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Thinking up the choreography and going through rehearsals with Miku‚ who we’ve always been fans of‚）\n（was an incredibly fulfilling experience.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.5183496046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi024.m4a",
      "text": "（その時間を）\n（会場のみんなとも分かち合えたら嬉しいな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I hope we can share）\n（that time with everyone here in the venue.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.6666833877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 221.6209436611
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
