      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 221.6209436611
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi025.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……これで北海道ともお別れか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… This is our farewell to Hokkaido‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 222.6709436611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi026.m4a",
      "text": "最初から最後までずっと慌ただしかったけど\n過ぎ去ってみれば、あっという間だったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was hectic from start to finish‚\nbut looking back‚ it went by in a flash.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.6000228245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 233.4915331559
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、ミクに会うとは思わなかったからなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never thought we’d meet Miku…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.4915331559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi027.m4a",
      "text": "いや、今回はいい経験になったよ\nまだまだ勉強しないといけないことが沢山あるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it was a good experience.\nThere’s still a lot we need to learn.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.7666894912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 244.5221004682
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "お、ステージの演出にも興味が出てきたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ are you getting interested in stage production now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.5221004682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi028.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね。センサーを使ったライトの演出も\n次こそちゃんと準備してやってみたいし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I want to properly prepare and try out\nthat lighting production with the sensors next time‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.4000228245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 255.350127367
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi029.m4a",
      "text": "ワイヤーで天井まで飛び上がるのもいいな\nミクみたいな、衣装の早着替えはさすがに難しいけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and I think it would be cool to fly up to the ceiling with wires.\nA quick costume change like Miku’s would be difficult‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.6333561579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 264.0405809281
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "……それは、早着替えの方がまだ簡単なんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I think the quick costume change might actually be easier…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.0405809281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi030.m4a",
      "text": "今度またミクに会った時には\nもっと成長した僕達を見てもらいたいからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next time we meet Miku‚\nI want her to see how much we’ve grown.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 271.3333561579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 274.6160009421
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_03-aoi031.m4a",
      "text": "そうして、また一緒にステージに立てたら嬉しいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would be great if we could stand on stage together again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 274.6160009421,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
